parts.text:
<OUTPUT_JSON>[
  {
    "selector": "table:has-text(\"order\" i) >> tr >> input[type=checkbox]",
    "action": "click",
    "description": "Select an order form by clicking its checkbox. Assumes clicking the first available if multiple match."
  },
  {
    "selector": "table:has-text(\"invoice\" i) >> tr >> input[type=checkbox]",
    "action": "click",
    "description": "Select an invoice by clicking its checkbox. Assumes clicking the first available if multiple match."
  },
  {
    "selector": "button:has-text(\"match\" i)",
    "action": "click",
    "description": "Click the 'match' button to match the selected order form and invoice."
  },
  {
    "selector": "button:has-text(\"record\" i)",
    "action": "click",
    "description": "Click the 'record' button to record the necessary information after matching."
  }
]</OUTPUT_JSON>
